quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,158,"Vane here chavangamirire kusara kwekuti ngirozi dziuye kwavari, kana kuti Tenzi vako vauye, kana kuti zvimwe zvezviratidzo zvaTenzi vako zviuye? Zuva iro zvimwe zvezviratidzo zvaTenzi vako zvichauya, hapana zvakanaka zvazvichaita kuti munhu atende ipapo, kana asina kutenda kumashure, kana kuita zvakanaka nokuda kwekutenda kwake. Iti: “Mirirai, zvirokwazvo isu takamirirawo.”"
  6,159,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanopatsanura chitendero chavo voita mapoka akasiyana, hauna (Muhammad (SAW)) chero chinhu chekuita navo. Zvirokwazvo, hwurongwa hwavo hwuna Allah, avo vachavaudza maererano neizvo zvavaiita"
  6,160,"Uyo anouya nebasa rimwe chete rakanaka, achava negumi akafanana naro (basa rimwe chete rakanaka), uye kune uyo anouya nebasa rimwe chete rakaipa, haapihwi mubairo kunze kwewakafanana naro (basa rakaipa), uye havasi kuzodzvanyirirwa"
  6,161,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vangu vakanditungamirira mugwara rakatwasuka, muchitendero chechokwadi, chitendero chaAbrahamu chakatwasuka (kutenda muhumwechete hwaAllah nekuvanamata vari voga), uye akanga asiri umwe wemaMushrikoon (avo vanosanganisa Allah nezvimwe zvinhu pakuvanamata).”"
  6,162,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Zvirokwazvo, munamato wangu, kupira kwangu, kurarama kwangu, uye nekufa kwangu ndezvaAllah, Tenzi vepasi rose.”"
  6,163,"“(Allah) havana mufambidzani. Uye kudaro ndakakomekedzwa, uye ndini wokutanga kune avo vakazvipira (maMuslim).”"
  6,164,"Iti: “Pane here wandingatsvage saTenzi kunze kwaAllah, vari ivo Tenzi wezvose? Hapana munhu anowana (chivi) kusara kwekuti chakanangana naiye. Uye hapana mutakuri wemutoro achatakura mutoro wemumwe. Zvakare kuna Tenzi venyu ndiko kwamuchadzokera, uye vokuudzai izvo zvamaipikisana.”"
  6,165,"Uye ndivo (Allah) vakakuitai vatevedzeri panyika (vamwe vachitsiva vamwe), uye vakakwidziridza vamwe venyu pazvidanho, vamwe pamusoro pevamwe, kuti vave vanokuedzai pane izvo zvavakakupai. Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako vanoranga nekuchimbidza, uye zvirokwazvo ndivo vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi zhinji"